{"tid":921051,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"招集想學Bass既巴絲","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T18:27:48.000Z","uid":144751,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ce6ea4ddb81c3fec37915c4399d22a4e3051bd","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"第一次出post<br />\n有咩講錯或者1999希望各位巴絲體諒<br />\n <br />\n我自己就彈左9年bass左右<br />\n年紀唔算好大  但都叫做彈過下演唱會 <br />\n幫人support下<br />\n例如做過小肥小胖等等藝人既session bassist<br />\n<br />\n幾年前開始搵學生<br />\n果時有啲免費或者收幾十蚊一個鐘都有<br />\n果時都唔係為收幾錢   <br />\n而係覺得當學生慢慢進步 就好有成功感<br />\n <br />\n除左教bass之外   <br />\n我都會寫下歌 編下曲 錄音 混音咁 <br />\n但最熟既都一定係bass <br />\n而自己都有挾band都有出左幾首歌<br />\nYouTube 同各大平台都有得聽<br />\n想聽既可以tg我<br />\n<br />\n呢排就抽到多啲時間出黎<br />\n想再收下學生  <br />\n都見有巴絲開po話想學但係又冇乜前輩開po <br />\n<br />\n價錢方面 <br />\n始終唔係跟琴行 唔洗比琴行定死價錢 有意可傾傾<br />\n同埋時間都可以自由啲控制<br />\n<br />\n至於教學方面<br />\n主要我會分3類學生<br />\n1.唔識    2.有concept  3.熟悉<br />\n<br />\n1. 對於bass毫無基礎既朋友仔<br />\n我會比較重點講手指練習 拍子練習 同埋記指板既音 同埋基本樂理<br />\n<br />\n2. 對於有 concept 知道bass已經大致做緊乜  <br />\n但又會比較多甩漏 或者 <br />\n需要多一啲練習既朋友仔<br />\n我就會係著重汁譜練習多啲 <br />\n一開始就比啲譜你彈下<br />\n慢慢開始要你自己汁譜<br />\n<br />\n3. 對於想成為職業bass手 <br />\n或者自己有挾開band 已經彈到好多歌<br />\n但到自己度bass line又好似差啲咁<br />\n我就會係不同風格 不同scale 上去做練習<br />\n因應同學仔想要 想學 中意啲咩風格<br />\n而去做番一啲專業練習 <br />\n而可以自己創作bass line<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果同學仔由唔識比我教到熟 <br />\n就會少啲touching 既問題<br />\n如果唔係由0開始既學生 <br />\n我都會比較著重touching<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有關於bass上既問題<br />\n可以留言或者tg我   我會儘量解答<br />\n如果對我既教學有興趣嘅話<br />\n亦歡迎tg詳談<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rcihcokw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frcihcokw&d=oW2ZKT0grFf0NVj5EkmC2P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3d106672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rcihcokw</a>"},{"pid":"b4b53c0a66670d3a3eff595d6e0326c00ff273c7","tid":921051,"uid":175783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"彈bass嘅都好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> g持"},{"pid":"3d062c3fd5a630549953259cf56b7cbe6a5fcfc9","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b475293bf077269a299d5b20da48cc134bc6ac","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T22:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a68b1ba533e560a51f48896732169125b6607b","tid":921051,"uid":166708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T22:10:43.000Z","msg":"結他佬幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29aeefe845898d879260c3633cb725279a0b5605","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f09a0ac502e8fb5f86a9d3f77144e72127ff9ac","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"喂！"},{"pid":"ffbdb7b38781975227b0da8c361ca1fec78f88c9","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9cab9b16cb050aef2d9746c6de6280b10ccd54","tid":921051,"uid":65343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"bass手幫推"},{"pid":"8bbca387588d341d2cd2b780fe6c146113bdf72d","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f228ad615f5e4b952f062978a8f0b38703718a97","tid":921051,"uid":144751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"